When you want to upload some files,
you need to download some software first, github and git shell
install them,
login,
clone your repository,
you will find a floder name as your repository,
add the new file into the floder,
runs the shell one.
type cd <name>
git status //check gile status
git add <name>//upload file
git commit -m "summary here"//commit and add summary


then you will find the right corner of github has "1" sign,
click syn,
after few seconds,
your files are upload successfully.
Done.
